commits.commitMessage:
Fix Release Client:
 1. ClientID will not be released once ReleaseClientID failed:
  a. resume ReleaseClientID after getting ClientID successfully.
 2. Client ID not release on UserSpaceCLose when group exit.
 3. mReleaseClientIDFail should not be assigned when process exit.
Fix Cleanup filp:
 1. gobi_filp_close to prevent process access invalid pointer:
  a. make file inode to bad.
  b. assign file to null.
Fix gobi_filp_close get blocked in UserspaceunlockedIOCTL and UserspaceWrite.
 1. Check device state before return ready in UserspacePoll.
Fix wakup_up_process crash
 1. Ignore wakup_up_process when current process is signaled group exit.

Resolves: LXQMIDRV-322

Signed-off-by: Alan Lam <alam@sierrawireless.com>

Change-Id: I43980c09143a3a56df153a2056887e42cb5e1be2
